data.description: Completely remodeled 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home nestled in a cul-de-sac street.  New floors, kitchen, bathrooms and lots of natural light. Conveniently close to shopping mall (Target, Walmart, Grocery Stores), restaurants, less than 2 miles to Chollas Lake & SDSU, minutes to Downtown San Diego and much more. Easy Freeway access. A must see!!
